snippet.title: Star Sign - Release Date Trailer | October 6, 2023
snippet.description:
I'm thrilled to announce that Star Sign will be released on October 6th, 2023. Be sure to add the game to your wishlist at https://store.steampowered.com/app/1860540/Star_Sign/

Follow the games progress at https://twitter.com/JoelObrist
Music by Jamie Henare: https://soundcloud.com/jamie-henare
